      • validateSettlementDt

        public Date validateSettlementDt(Date paramSettlementDt,
                                 String paramCurrencyType)
                          throws TradingSystemException
        This method is used to validate the settlement date where it is holiday based on the currency and assign the next work day to the settlement date
        Parameters:
        paramSettlementDt - This parameter contains the Settlement date to be validated.
        paramCurrencyType - This parameter contains the Currency for that settlement.
        Returns:
        It returns the date object of the valid Settlement Date.
        Throws:
        TradingSystemException - This exception throws when Settlement date or Currency has null values.
